metadata.name: With such a group of people
metadata.description:
In the face of such a situation, even experienced special forces, but also helpless.



"Dragon Boat Festival, to the city to be careful. This is not like our house. Duck when you see a bullet. If you were dead, I wouldn't be able to go back to your father and your mother."



At this moment, the old calabash was whispering in the ear of Dragon Boat Festival, accompanied by the little Hubei who was less than one meter and four.



Small Hubei raises a face, that look in the eyes is full of worship.
